Welcome to RELAX Engine Project for TOOSHEH TV
This program automatically extract recorded TS file on UBIX Server. You must first set some parameters in Config file via setting tab to work program correctly.For TS files you need recorded file on shared network path or your local hard drive. program first copy files from server or shared location to client and then do jobs.for each current day you should have only one TS file in source directory.If source folder contains more than one file, Engine merged the output files in output folder. We are working hard to release better versions and fix bugs day by day.
